I change hibernate dependency in pom.xml
from
```
        &lt;dependency&gt;
            &lt;groupId&gt;org.hibernate&lt;/groupId&gt;
            &lt;artifactId&gt;hibernate-validator&lt;/artifactId&gt;
            &lt;version&gt;7.0.1.Final&lt;/version&gt;
