to

```
&lt;dependency&gt;
    &lt;groupId&gt;org.hibernate.validator&lt;/groupId&gt;
    &lt;artifactId&gt;hibernate-validator&lt;/artifactId&gt;
    &lt;version&gt;6.1.5.Final&lt;/version&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;
```

